title: Female Fronted Japanese Metal
description:
Here is a small kinda update to some of the Japanese female fronted Metal videos i have already uploaded.
Most are 720p and a few are 480p but excellent video nonetheless.

2 or 3 are also music video samples because i could not find full versions anywhere.
But there pretty cool and they give you an idea if this sorta genre is your cup of tea.

All are female fronted except for Exist Trace in which i have questions and doubts about the singer being female but who knows.LOL

Needless to say its all good!

Please SEED and Enjoy

Pitufo7777
